EFL Back of the net Tottenham’s net spend over last five years is just £1MILLION, putting Manchester City’s outrageous £402.5million to shame 
White Hart Lane outfit has only spent £1million more than they've raised in transfers since 2012, a far cry from the rest of the Premier League By Dave Fraser
